Bug ID : HP_BugR1

Test Case ID : TC_HP6

Title : Missing Language adjustment option
 
Environment : Windows 10, Firefox Build 147.0.4(64-Bit)

Prerequisites : none

Severity : Major

Priority : High

Description : User is unable to adjust or change the language settings of the website. 

Steps to Reproduce : 
1.Open https://www.mcdonalds.com/de/de-de.html
2. (Optional) Use search functionality of web browser to look for language settings.

Expected Result : Language settings are visible and easily reachable for end-user.

Actual Result : No language settings available

Status : Open

Assigned To : -

Comments : Adjusting Language settings provides customers with low technical and language knowledge the possibility to access and use the website as intended.
